Gridspot,can,link,up,idle,computers,instances,across,the,world,to,provide,large,scale,efforts,with,the,computing,power,they,require,at,affordable,prices,cents,CPU,hour,These,Linux,instances,run,Ubuntu,inside,a,virtual,machine,You,are,able,to,bid,on,access,to,these,instances,and,specify,the,requirements,of,your,tasks,or,jobs,When,your,bid,is,fulfilled,you,can,start,running,the,instances,using,SSH,anywhere,you,d,like,There,are,grant,options,available,to,defray,costs,for,researchers,and,non,profits,The,Gridspot,API,allows,you,to,manage,instances,and,identify,new,ones,You,can,list,available,instances,access,them,and,stop,the,instances,if,you,so,choose,Each,API,call,requires,an,API,key,that,can,be,generated,from,your,account,page